And I really enjoyed it.<br>
It was funny as a hell, but also scary and creepy.<br>
And John Constantine is just  a magnificent character.<br>
After reading all those issues there is still just one thing, that keeps bugging me.<br>
Why is there never any real meeting between Lucifer and Constatntine ?<br>
And does Hellblazer play in the same Universe as Lucifer?<br>
